# Mazonkiki Admin Assistant

Claude-powered Shopify admin tool for mazonkiki.com — SEO editing, schema generation, theme editing, redirect management, and debugging.

## Deploy to Vercel (5 minutes)

### 1. Create GitHub repo
- Go to github.com → New repository
- Name: `mazonkiki-admin`
- Private repository
- Upload all files from this folder

### 2. Connect to Vercel
- Go to vercel.com → Add New Project
- Import your `mazonkiki-admin` GitHub repo
- Click Deploy (it will fail first time — that's ok, we need env vars)

### 3. Add environment variables
In Vercel dashboard → Your project → Settings → Environment Variables, add:

| Name | Value |
|---|---|
| `SHOPIFY_TOKEN` | Your Shopify access token (shpat_...) |
| `ANTHROPIC_KEY` | Your Anthropic API key (sk-ant-...) |
| `STORE_URL` | `mazonkiki.myshopify.com` |

### 4. Redeploy
- Go to Deployments → click the three dots → Redeploy
- Your app will be live at `https://mazonkiki-admin-xxxx.vercel.app`

## Features

- 💬 **AI Chat** — Claude assistant with full store context and audit findings
- 🔍 **SEO Editor** — Edit meta titles, descriptions, alt text, URL handles, metafields per product
- ⚡ **Schema Generator** — Generate Organization, Product, and FAQ schema JSON-LD
- 🎨 **Theme Editor** — View and edit Shopify theme Liquid files
- 🔗 **Redirect Manager** — Create and manage 301 redirects
- 🐛 **Debug Console** — Inspect any product's full data, run GraphQL queries

## Security
- All API keys stored as Vercel environment variables (never in code)
- App is private — share the URL only with yourself
- No data stored — all reads/writes go directly to Shopify
